Title: Ground State Structure of a Coupled 2-Fermion System in Supersymmetric

Quantum MechanicsAuthors: Felix Finster (Harvard University, Department of Mathematics)

Comments: 8 pages, LaTex

Journal-ref: Annals Phys. 256 (1997) 135-143

We prove the uniqueness of the ground state for a supersymmetric quantummechanical system of two fermions and two bosons, which is closely related tothe N=1 WZ-model. The proof is constructive and gives detailed information onwhat the ground state looks like.